				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ppf
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = pjw
									value = 0.001
								}
							}
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ppf
									value = 0.001
								}
							}
						}
						divide_variable = { 
							which = pjw
							which = ppf
						}
						multiply_variable = { 
							which = pjw
							value = 100
						}
					}
					if = {

country_event = { 
	id = POP_DG.005
	title = "no_localisation"
	desc = "no_localisation"
	picture = MEIOU_AND_TAXES_eventPicture
	is_triggered_only = yes
	hidden = yes
	immediate = { 
		every_country = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					num_of_cities = 1
					NOT = { 
						tag = AAA
					}
				}
				ai = yes
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					OR = { 
						AND = { 
							AAA = { 
								has_country_flag = biannual
							}
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = rhx
									which = rii
								}
							}
						}
						AND = { 
							AAA = { 
								NOT = { 
									has_country_flag = biannual
								}
							}
							NOT = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = rhx
										which = rii
									}
								}
							}
						}
					}
				}
				trigger_switch = { 
					on_trigger = religion
					catholic = { 
						every_owned_province = { 
							trigger_switch = { 
								on_trigger = has_province_flag
								catholic_archbishopric = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											NOT = { 
												has_province_modifier = catholic_archbishopric
											}
										}
										add_province_modifier = { 
											name = catholic_archbishopric
											duration = -1
											hidden = yes
										}
									}
								}
							}
						}
					}
					protestant = { }
					reformed = { }
					hussite = { }
					waldensian = { }
					lollard = { }
					avignonist = { }
					holyleague = { }
					orthodox = { 
						country_event = { 
							id = DG_Orthodox.001
						}
						every_owned_province = { 
							trigger_switch = { 
								on_trigger = has_province_flag
								orthodox_patriarchate = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											NOT = { 
												has_province_modifier = orthodox_patriarchate
											}
										}
										add_province_modifier = { 
											name = orthodox_patriarchate
											duration = -1
											hidden = yes
										}
									}
								}
								orthodox_archbishopric = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											NOT = { 
												has_province_modifier = orthodox_archbishopric
											}
										}
										add_province_modifier = { 
											name = orthodox_archbishopric
											duration = -1
											hidden = yes
										}
									}
								}
								orthodox_metropolitan = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											NOT = { 
												has_province_modifier = orthodox_metropolitan
											}
										}
										add_province_modifier = { 
											name = orthodox_metropolitan
											duration = -1
											hidden = yes
										}
									}
								}
							}
							trigger_switch = { 
								on_trigger = has_province_flag
								cenobitic_monastery = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											NOT = { 
												has_province_modifier = cenobitic_monastery
											}
										}
										add_province_modifier = { 
											name = cenobitic_monastery
											duration = -1
											hidden = yes
										}
									}
								}
								lavra_monastery = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											NOT = { 
												has_province_modifier = lavra_monastery
											}
										}
										add_province_modifier = { 
											name = lavra_monastery
											duration = -1
											hidden = yes
										}
									}
								}
								stavropegic_monastery = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											NOT = { 
												has_province_modifier = stavropegic_monastery
											}
										}
										add_province_modifier = { 
											name = stavropegic_monastery
											duration = -1
											hidden = yes
										}
									}
								}
								monastic_town = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											NOT = { 
												has_province_modifier = monastic_town
											}
										}
										add_province_modifier = { 
											name = monastic_town
											duration = -1
											hidden = yes
										}
									}
								}
							}
						}
					}
					oriental = { }
					assyrian = { }
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "no_localisation"
	}
}

								add_province_modifier = { 
									name = lavra_monastery
									duration = -1
									hidden = yes
								}
							}
						}
						stavropegic_monastery = { 
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									NOT = { 
										has_province_modifier = stavropegic_monastery
									}
								}
								add_province_modifier = { 
									name = stavropegic_monastery
									duration = -1
									hidden = yes
								}
							}
						}
						monastic_town = { 
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									NOT = { 
										has_province_modifier = monastic_town
									}
								}
								add_province_modifier = { 
									name = monastic_town
									duration = -1
									hidden = yes
								}
							}
						}
					}
				}
			}
			oriental = { }
			assyrian = { }
		}
	}
}

						remove_province_modifier = MN_A_64
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = kdt
									value = 32
								}
							}
						}
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 32
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								NOT = { 
									has_province_modifier = MN_A_32
								}
							}
							add_province_modifier = { 
								name = MN_A_32
								duration = -1
								hidden = yes
							}
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							has_province_modifier = MN_A_32
						}
						remove_province_modifier = MN_A_32
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = kdt
									value = 16
								}
							}
						}
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 16
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								NOT = { 
									has_province_modifier = MN_A_16
								}
							}
							add_province_modifier = { 
								name = MN_A_16
								duration = -1
								hidden = yes
							}
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							has_province_modifier = MN_A_16
						}
						remove_province_modifier = MN_A_16
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = kdt
									value = 8
								}
							}
						}
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 8
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								NOT = { 
									has_province_modifier = MN_A_8
								}
							}
							add_province_modifier = { 
								name = MN_A_8
								duration = -1
								hidden = yes
							}
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							has_province_modifier = MN_A_8
						}
						remove_province_modifier = MN_A_8
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = kdt
									value = 4
								}
							}
						}
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 4
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								NOT = { 
									has_province_modifier = MN_A_4
								}
							}
							add_province_modifier = { 
								name = MN_A_4
								duration = -1
								hidden = yes
							}

					}
					else_if = {

					if = {

									which = kdt
									value = 2
								}
							}

							value = 2

							}
						}

province_event = { 
	id = POP_DG.101
	title = "AI_Event"
	desc = "AI_Event"
	picture = INVENTION_eventPicture
	hidden = yes
	fire_only_once = yes
	trigger = { 
		religion_group = christian
		owner = { 
			adm_tech = 25
			religion_group = christian
		}
		Banking = 100
		NOT = { 
			has_global_flag = printing_press_g
		}
		AND = { 
			check_variable = { 
				which = gcj
				value = 2
			}
		}
		is_capital = yes
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 1
	}
	immediate = { 
		owner = { 
			set_global_flag = printing_press_g
			set_country_flag = printing_press_c
			add_reform_desire = 0.0005
		}
		set_province_flag = printing_press_p
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				OR = { 
					superregion = germany_superregion
					superregion = scandinavian_superregion
				}
			}
			save_global_event_target_as = ger_printing_press
			set_global_flag = DG_German_Printing_Press
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				superregion = france_superregion
			}
			save_global_event_target_as = fra_printing_press
			set_global_flag = DG_French_Printing_Press
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				superregion = iberia_superregion
			}
			save_global_event_target_as = ibe_printing_press
			set_global_flag = DG_Iberian_Printing_Press
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				superregion = italy_superregion
			}
			save_global_event_target_as = ita_printing_press
			set_global_flag = DG_Italian_Printing_Press
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				superregion = british_isles_superregion
			}
			save_global_event_target_as = eng_printing_press
			set_global_flag = DG_English_Printing_Press
		}
		PAP = { 
			export_to_variable = { 
				which = printing_press_year
				value = trigger_value:is_year
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		province_event = { 
			id = POP_DG.102
			days = 1
		}
	}
}
province_event = { 
	id = POP_DG.102
	title = "POP_DG.101.title"
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_German_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.101.dger"
	}
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_French_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.101.dfra"
	}
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_Iberian_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.101.dibe"
	}
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_Italian_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.101.dita"
	}
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_English_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.101.deng"
	}
	picture = INVENTION_eventPicture
	fire_only_once = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "POP_DG.101.opta"
		owner = { 
			add_adm_power = 50
		}
		owner = { 
			add_dip_power = 50
		}
		owner = { 
			add_mil_power = 50
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "POP_DG.101.optb"
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = ahf
				value = 600
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						stability = 3
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
				}
				else = { 
					subtract_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
					add_stability = 1
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ahf
								value = 0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							stability = -2
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 0
					}
				}
				else = { 
					change_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
					add_stability = -1
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				which = ahf
			}
			divide_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 12
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 0.1
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 10
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = lsc
				value = 100
			}
			subtract_variable = { 
				which = lsc
				which = ahd
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_StabAdd50
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				is_emperor_of_china = yes
			}
			add_mandate = 2.5
		}
	}
	after = { 
		province_event = { 
			id = POP_DG.103
			days = 27
			random = 10
		}
	}
}

	id = POP_DG.104
	title = "POP_DG.103.title"
	desc = {

			has_global_flag = DG_German_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.103.dger"
	}
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_French_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.103.dfra"
	}
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_Iberian_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.103.dibe"
	}
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_Italian_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.103.dita"
	}
	desc = { 
		trigger = { 
			has_global_flag = DG_English_Printing_Press
		}
		desc = "POP_DG.103.deng"
	}
	picture = INVENTION_eventPicture
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "POP_DG.103.opta"

			factor = 30
			modifier = { 
				capital_distance = { 
					who = PAP
					distance = 260
				}
				factor = 2
			}
			modifier = { 
				capital_distance = { 
					who = PAP
					distance = 390
				}
				factor = 2
			}
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					capital_distance = { 
						who = PAP
						distance = 130
					}
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				OR = { 
					is_emperor = yes
					any_known_country = { 
						is_elector = yes
						preferred_emperor = ROOT
					}
				}
				NOT = { 
					any_known_country = { 
						is_elector = yes
						religion = protestant
					}
				}
				factor = 0.2
			}
			modifier = { 
				is_papal_controller = yes
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				num_of_loans = 1
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				num_of_loans = 2
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_neighbor_country = { 
					NOT = { 
						religion_group = christian
					}
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_neighbor_country = { 
					NOT = { 
						religion = catholic
					}
					NOT = { 
						religion = protestant
					}
					NOT = { 
						religion = reformed
					}
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					OR = { 
						religion = hussite
						religion = gnostic
						religion = protestant
						religion = reformed
					}
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				dominant_religion = protestant
				factor = 2
			}
			modifier = { 
				government = republic
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				capital_scope = { 
					superregion = france_superregion
				}
				factor = 0.1
			}
			modifier = { 
				capital_scope = { 
					superregion = italy_superregion
				}
				factor = 0
			}
			modifier = { 
				capital_scope = { 
					superregion = iberia_superregion
				}
				factor = 0
			}
			modifier = { 
				capital_scope = { 
					superregion = germany_superregion
				}
				factor = 2.75
			}
			modifier = { 
				capital_scope = { 
					superregion = balkan_superregion
				}
				factor = 1.1
			}
			modifier = { 
				government = theocracy
				capital_scope = { 
					superregion = commonwealth_superregion
				}
				factor = 3.00
			}
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					government = theocracy
				}
				capital_scope = { 
					superregion = commonwealth_superregion
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				factor = 2.75
				capital_scope = { 
					superregion = scandinavian_superregion
				}
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = ata
					value = -10
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = atb
					value = -10
				}
				if = { 
					limit = {
